me":"2019-10-06T17:28:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"},{"pid":"62ab9ce95945c12d8e4bf4cb88204e75d9e1d832","tid":1632233,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:14.000Z","msg":"美國民意都叫唔好打貿戰喇，侵侵根本wfc <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcfc22ecdc96e3697c15cd953db07da2dda2545","tid":1632233,"uid":147785,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"17125693dc367e771dccd64926f3bedf04d27514","tid":1632233,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得你先係分化五毛狗喎<br />\n人地成篇野好有道理，唔要國際戰線既話不如你開個post叫攬炒巴收皮摺埋啦傻閪<br />\n早啲返屋企啦阿蛇，你老婆好多手足屌緊呀，快啲返去排隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:02.000Z","msg":"係咁話前線無智慧<br />\n<br />\n邊個先係真分化呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3666ed4ce25134d6fac5a1f8a31b56b4e84008b","tid":1632233,"uid":55130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a2475699c6c765284941adf15c00cd3c1e6f49d","tid":1632233,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:06.000Z","msg":"屌前線on9 丶痴線丶失控一律視為三毛/狗"},{"pid":"dedc748547c331fc8d7abc3052479e3f1b5c5eb4","tid":1632233,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17125693dc367e771dccd64926f3bedf04d27514","tid":1632233,"uid":706,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:26:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得你先係分化五毛狗喎<br />\n人地成篇野好有道理，唔要國際戰線既話不如你開個post叫攬炒巴收皮摺埋啦傻閪<br />\n早啲返屋企啦阿蛇，你老婆好多手足屌緊呀，快啲返去排隊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:31:23.000Z","msg":"我係咪分化<br />\n<br />\n你起我底 + 起佢底 都略知一二啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e74b314c11c887e96f56d5041fa9cc987736656","tid":1632233,"uid":288707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bcaca9cfc27c65f9f76698446d9ae2d62ec5978b","tid":1632233,"uid":147785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:21:24.000Z","msg":"btw<br />\n<br />\n我個人係同意 勇武應該忍一忍手幾日<br />\n<br />\n比文宣帶番風向先 +拖多陣時間<br />\n<br />\n日日18區 文宣無可能跟得切"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:08.000Z","msg":"18區唱歌啦"},{"pid":"78196dac0a784150e12a452879839659d710ecae","tid":1632233,"uid":75823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:54.000Z","msg":"要用政治角度估下五毛既目標<br />\n<br />\n將前線極端化, 想前線END GAME, 最多亂幾日, 但就可以一次拉哂 (講緊一晚五百人至一千人, 會對我地士氣極大破壞), 係對政府最有利<br />\n<br />\n叫停前線, 即使令局勢平靜, 表面對政府有利, 但其實係保存左前線力量, 咁係對政府中長遠不利<br />\n<br />\n咁樣自然知道五毛會講咩野"}]}